problem_text: If Q R \parallel X Y, X Q \cong Q Z, and Q R = 9.5 units, what is the length of X Y.
compact_text: If QR \parallel XY, XQ \cong QZ, and QR = 9.5 units, what is the length of XY.
annotat_text: If $\overline{QR} \| \overline{XY}, \overline{XQ} \cong \overline{QZ}$, and $QR=9.5$ units, what is the length of $\overline{XY}$.
